data.description: Nestled within the serene embrace of nature lies a charming three-level cabin, a sanctuary of rustic elegance on a sprawling 20-acre estate. The exterior of the cabin includes 6 water spickets, a 50' X 25' detached garage, 12' X 24' hay stalls, 9' X 45' conex box, 11' X 44' pole barn, 3-acre pasture, garden with a garden shed, a working out-house with septic, 12 raised beds, horseshoe pit and Bocce ball court.
